ored meat.  I'm dead serious.", :release_date => "1995-07-28", :title => "Super Bonk 2", :developer => "Hudson Soft", :publisher => "Hudson Soft", :coverart_remote_url => 'http://thegamesdb.net/banners/boxart/original/front/18805-1.jpg')
